text: Abdelraouf al-Rawabdeh (; born 18 February 1939) is a Jordanian politician. He was the Prime Minister of Jordan from 4 March 1999 until 19 June 2000. On 24 October 2013 he was named President of the Senate. He resigned on 25 October 2015. ==References== Rawabdeh Category:Living people Category:1939 births
